                            <comment id="13906344" author="elserj" created="Thu, 20 Feb 2014 00:17:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Both hadoop1 and hadoop2 fail when I try to put the timeout on the JUnit Test annotation, and both work when the timeout is not present. I&apos;m guessing that the ScriptState ThreadLocal is getting initialized differently when JUnit is running the test with the timeout. Patch removes the test exclusion and removes the commented out timeout.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13906443" author="daijy" created="Thu, 20 Feb 2014 01:28:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Verified it works. Patch committed to trunk. Thanks Josh!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
